data.description: Location! Location! Location! This townhome is located just minutes from the Oaks Mall and directly on the bus route with a stop at the entrance. This 2/2 is an end unit and features a split floor plan with one bedroom and an updated bathroom down stairs and one bedroom and bathroom upstairs with an additional loft area for small office or study.  The kitchen features custom wood cabinets, under mount sink, and granite on counters and pass through window. Other features of the home are laminate wood flooring in the main area, an open dining room/ living room combination , separate laundry room, screen porch, private courtyard in the front and close to the swimming pool and tennis courts. This is a nice unit in a great location and wont last long so make an appointment to see it today!
